                {
                <div class="help-module" id="module-reports" data-keywords="report export excel pdf collection settlement expense client due analytics">
                    <div class="help-module-header">
                        <div class="help-module-icon" style="background:#f3e8ff;color:#9333ea;"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line"></i></div>
                        <div>
                            <h3>Reports</h3>
                            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:.78rem;">Business intelligence with Excel & PDF exports</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="module-badge">All Users</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>The Reports module offers ready-made analytical reports for various business functions. All reports support date-range filtering and can be exported to <strong>Excel</strong> or <strong>PDF</strong> formats for offline analysis and sharing.</p>
                    <ol class="help-steps">
                        <li><strong>Client Details Report</strong> — A comprehensive listing of all client information and licence details.</li>
                        <li><strong>Expense Report</strong> — Analyze expense spending by category, department, or date range.</li>
                        <li><strong>Settlement Report</strong> — View details of reimbursement settlements processed by Finance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Daily Collection Register</strong> — Track daily revenue collections against invoices. Non-admin users see only their own collections; Admins can filter by collector.</li>
                        <li><strong>Client Due Report</strong> — View outstanding balances and overdue invoices across all clients.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="help-features">
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Date Range Filters</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Excel Export</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> PDF Export</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> User-scoped Access</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Server-side Paging</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="help-tip">
                        <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill"></i>
                        <div><strong>Tip:</strong> In the Daily Collection Register, non-admin users see only their own data. Admins get a "Collected By" dropdown to filter by any user.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
