                        <li>Set the <strong>Company Name</strong> (displayed in the sidebar branding and footer).</li>
                        <li>Upload a <strong>Company Logo</strong> for sidebar branding.</li>
                        <li>Configure address, GST, and other company information used in documents.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="help-features">
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> User CRUD</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Multi-role Assignment</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Profile Images</div>
                        <div class="help-feature-tag"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Company Branding</div>
