                    <ol class="help-steps">
                        <li><strong>Email Configuration</strong> — Set up SMTP server details (Host, Port, Username, Password, SSL/TLS). Navigate to <strong>Administration → Email Engine</strong>.</li>
                        <li><strong>Email Templates</strong> — Create and manage dynamic email templates with placeholder variables. Templates are used automatically by various modules (e.g., licence expiry notification, invoice email).</li>
                        <li><strong>Email Logs</strong> — View a complete audit trail of all sent emails. Filter by date range and email type. Useful for debugging delivery issues.</li>
