                        <li><strong>Sidebar Collapse</strong> — Click the <i class="bi bi-list"></i> hamburger menu to collapse/expand the sidebar for more workspace.</li>
                        <li><strong>Role Switching</strong> — If you have multiple roles, use the "Switch Role" dropdown in the topbar to change your active role without logging out.</li>
